<voice_0x010013F9><center>You are brave enough to follow my shadow
<center>and enter the realm of light.
<center>And you are a fine fighter.

<voice_0x010013FA><center>As you know,
<center>this game is a difficult test.

<voice_0x010013FB><center>Excuse me,
<center>I'm looking for someone strong to help me...
<voice_0x010013FC><se_low>King of tricks: You don't think we are dealing with village thugs?
<voice_0x010013FD><se_low>King of tricks: Please forgive me I do not understand. I will not assist in your evil plans!

<voice_0x010013FE><center>don't make me wrong
<center>The idea of invading the country
never crossed my mind.
<voice_0x010013FF><center>This is one reason why I need help.

<voice_0x01001400><center>When Dark Lord Lapson
<center>tried to stop the light,
<center>the Elders helped drive him away.

<voice_0x01001401><center>Thus, we destroyed the enemy Giant Rapthorn
<center>and that's how we were left in this situation.

<voice_0x01001402><center>In the nest,
<center>chicks and eggs are waiting to hatch.

<voice_0x01001403><center>But Zemun, one of the evil helpers
<center>of the Lappish throne, got the better of me.
<center>They took my penis hostage.

<voice_0x01001404><center>This has led to people attacking the city
<center>they live in. You can't say "no"
<center>if you want to help the children.

<voice_0x01001405><center>when an ordinary person comes in front of you
<center>you won't be afraid of anything
<center>But if you have the courage you will do nothing

<voice_0x01001406><center>So I have to find somebody to protect me.
<center>Strong and courageous person

<voice_0x01001407><center>You followed my shadow
<center>into the dark world without hesitation,
<center>such courage is rare.

<voice_0x01001408><center>You have now proven yourself on the battlefield.
<center>Undoubtedly, you were the only strong
<center>and brave man who defeated Jammu.

<voice_0x01001409><center>Leave an egg for me and the unborn child.
<center>and the inhabitants of this island
<voice_0x0100140A><se_low>King of tricks: Hear my son <hero>! I can't ignore a woman's plea... birds... ladybugs... oh explosions and chaos!
<voice_0x0100140B><se_low>King of tricks: In my opinion, there is no reason not to help those in need!
<voice_0x0100140C><se_low>King of tricks: Don't worry, ma'am, I was asked to find your ball.
<voice_0x0100140D><center>Thank you for your vote.

<voice_0x0100140E><center>I live on the rock
<center>of an inaccessible peak.

<voice_0x0100140F><center>Since Goemon is watching,
<center>I can't take you far away,
<center>but I can take you to the mountains.
<voice_0x01001410><center>Ready to get started?

<voice_0x01001411><center>waiting for you here
<center>Tell me when you are done.

<voice_0x01001412><center>“I am impatient.” I will take you.
<center>Will you follow the trend,
<center>or will you wait?
<voice_0x01001413><center>hold on

<voice_0x01001414><center>I understand
<center>let's go

<voice_0x01001415><center>Could you guide me to the foot
<center>of the mountain where my cave is?
<voice_0x01001416><center>going

<voice_0x0100141B><center>Being here meant that the door
<center>to the Light World was still open.

<voice_0x0100141C><center>A long time ago, during the battle
<center>with the Demon Lord, I lost the ability
<center>to return to the original world.
<center>But now it appears to be slowly recovering.
<voice_0x0100141D><center>Maybe it's time that I need you again

<voice_0x0100141E><center>But there must be some reason
<center>why he came here.

<voice_0x0100141F><center>Would you like to go back to the mountain
<center>where you swam for the first time?

<voice_0x01001420><center>If necessary, we will redirect you
<center>to the main topic.
<center>Hop in or wait.

<voice_0x01001421><center>Remarks<:> May I go with you?
<center>Sorry, that's all I can do right now...

<voice_0x01001422><center>When I regain my strength,
<center>I will definitely help. We are sorry
<center>but we cannot help you at the moment.

<voice_0x01001423><center>Elements
<center>Have you decided to return to your home?

<voice_0x01001420><center>If necessary, we will redirect you
<center>to the main topic.
<center>Hop in or wait.
